---
title: Quick Double Thai-Style Chicken & Creamy Slaw with Sweet Chilli Sauce & Coriander
description: When it gets chilli out, it’s a good idea to have an extra layer on you, but how about on tonight’s dinner? Let’s add layers upon layers of flavour by coating the chicken in our Southeast Asian spices. The slaw joins in by getting wrapped in a sesame ginger dressing. For the finishing touch, dollop over some warming sweet chilli sauce!
